jumpingjacks.md: If you are able to, do *30 seconds* of *jumping jacks*. Common alternatives may include marching in place or doing a brisk walk. The point is to get your heart rate up and blood flowing through your body.
jumpingjacks.title: Jumping Jacks

pushups.md: If you are able to, do *15 Push-Ups*. Common alternatives may include Knee Push-Ups or Inclined Push-Ups. Just make sure your heart starts beating a bit faster and you feel your muscle engorging to some degree.
pushups.title: Push-Ups
